---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Terms · Griffino" description="Terms placeholder for griffino.cc." path="/terms.html">
  <main class="content-page">
    <p class="eyebrow">Terms</p>
    <h1>Terms of Use</h1>
    <p class="hero-copy">This page is a placeholder terms version for griffino.cc. Griffino is still in pre-release; the formal terms of service should be added once public release, community governance, and distribution mechanisms stabilize.</p>

    <section class="content-section">
      <h2>Open Source License</h2>
      <p>The core Griffino repositories use the Apache-2.0 license. SDKs, schemas, the plugin center, and third-party plugins may carry their own licenses and NOTICE files; refer to the corresponding repositories.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section">
      <h2>No Warranty</h2>
      <p>Current project materials, code, and documentation are provided as-is for an open-source project and may change between versions. Please assess security, stability, and compliance requirements yourself before using them in production or sensitive environments.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section">
      <h2>Contributions and Content</h2>
      <p>When submitting issues, pull requests, or plugins, contributors should ensure they have the right to submit the relevant content and avoid including keys, sensitive personal information, restricted data, or materials that infringe third-party rights.</p>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
